T01:27:59+08:00</updated><content>是时候重新审视身份认同与工作之间的联系了。</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&amp;mid=2650093897&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0751367840efa66910ad7522639b4679&amp;chksm=bed7d0fb89a059ed6c061da2695e5b4f164fcbb2789a71d44c79d41d321f73ddc397421eba97&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>0aec0ae7d7482fc5a6cda7129495c318</id><title>迎合别人还是做自己，70%的人选错了</title><updated>2020-04-23T08:09:08+08:00</updated><content>迎合对方反而远不如做真实的自己有效</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&amp;mid=2650093886&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=198dd0f7ae466c2a4600146377e4df12&amp;chksm=bed7d08c89a0599aa84d2fb56efa8ec41661814a170f042c866facebcfd223d68c98d9971877&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>36bf022133566b8ab7918611cef0d078</id><title>世界读书日 哈佛商学院院长请你来读书！</title><updated>2020-04-23T08:09:08+08:00</updated><content>——世界商学院大牛亲荐书单</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&amp;mid=2650093886&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=d83cbcb7d00ce4cefc3404557c6723eb&amp;chksm=bed7d08c89a0599ab1266dcfa52db4bca1db8812d0a3684bff134c08269b66ff5b08dc8068bf&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>d41ba9a52745aaf877cc3db89e24a9c7</id><title>2020 NAVIGATE领航者峰会云上启航 | 推广</title><updated>2020-04-22T01:08:19+08:00</updated><content>4月20日，由紫光集团和旗下新华三集团主办的2020 NAVIGATE领航者峰会盛大启航。</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&amp;mid=2650093846&amp;idx=3&amp;sn=58c4da0861e4252b7396e5ea4b61f28c&amp;chksm=bed7d0a489a059b23422cb2ded26bb678e1a05ad4a8abeaf1d19720ae3916eb5c07aff1c9a0c&amp;scene=0&amp;xtrack=1#rd" rel="alternate"/></entry><entry><id>b237dda4f3b340f41bdea179d280bef0</id><title>港科大MBA网络示范课和线上宣讲会报名中 | 特别策划</title><updated>2020-04-22T01:08:19+08:00</updated><content>港科大MBA宣讲会来袭！</content><link href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NzY4MzQyMQ==&amp;mid=2650093846&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=19d3e834c32a10e2eabfc55630f0e1d8&amp;chksm=bed7d0a489a059b2c7b366988edad